method is trivially simple: `target_step = (E2E_mean - TTFT_mean) / output_len_mean`, then decompose into beta0 (overhead floor) + beta2 * decode_tokens.\n\nHowever, the \"hybrid\" hypothesis is wrong — CMA-ES residual tuning makes things worse, not better, because the base model is already E2E-optimal.\n\n### Artifacts Produced\n\n- **FINDINGS_SUMMARY.md** with all 10 required sections (including Generalization, Section 10)\n- **4 FINDINGS.md** files (one per sub-hypothesis)\n- **Per-model StepML JSON artifacts** in h1-principled-base/output/artifacts/\n- **BLIS validation CSVs** for H1, H2, H3, H4\n- **Go patch file** for `--stepml-model` CLI integration\n- **grand_summary.json** with all numerical results","stop_reason":null,"session_id":"e652145f-d03b-4eb5-bbf8-d7db257fe10a","total_cost_usd":3.0619639999999992,"usage":{"input_tokens":22834,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":39735,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001":{"inputTokens":96599,"outputTokens":3313,"cacheReadInputTokens":0,"cacheCreationInputTokens":0,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.11316399999999995,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTokens":32000},"aws/claude-opus-4-6":{"inputTokens":64875,"outputTokens":104977,"cacheReadInputTokens":0,"cacheCreationInputTokens":0,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":2.9488,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTokens":32000}},"permission_denials":[],"uuid":"25347e21-9957-41de-8ce5-130ed83aebd9"}
